{"type":null,"faqId":45002,"title":"收到短信无声音","answer":"<body style=\"clear:both; padding-left:10px; padding-top:5px; padding-right:5px; padding-bottom:5px\"><div id=\"body50520525\"><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033310543__p5460191494212\">1、请确认是否所有界面都没有提示（当前安卓原生设计：在短信会话的信息详情界面该联系人来短信，不会有响铃提示）。</p><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033310543__p2165518194212\">2、请确认是否开启铃声音量（按手机侧键增大手机音量）。</p><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033310543__p6067890894212\">3、请检查短信提示音设置是否正确</p><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033310543__p923926294212\">EMUI 3.1：<strong id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033310543__b1604450294212\">信息&gt;菜单&gt;设置&gt;通用&gt;提示音</strong>，检查是否设置提示音。</p><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033310543__p1018279694212\">EMUI 4.0：<strong id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033310543__b2453630594212\">信息&gt;菜单&gt;设置&gt;选择铃声</strong>，检查是否选择为“无”。</p><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033310543__p1950015894212\">4、请检查是否开启免打扰功能。</p><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033310543__p4128370194212\">5、<strong id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033310543__b3600898994212\">手机管家&gt;通知中心&gt;信息</strong>，查看<strong id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033310543__b5564544894212\">允许通知</strong>是否开启。</p><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033310543__p3104699294212\">6、请重启手机尝试。</p><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033310543__p1098747794212\">7、如果还不能解决问题，请备份重要数据后恢复出厂设置。</p></div></body>","faqTypeId":139,"faqType":"应用程序管理","useful":1,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"zh-cn_topic_0033310543","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Application-Management","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442409481000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":11,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"短信没声音,信息无提示声,短消息无声,短信静音","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}